<MudText Typo="Typo.h6" Class="mt-5">Rules and Information</MudText>

<MudText Class="mt-2">
    There will be many caches hidden around camp with a qr code on them.
    Click the button to scan a cache and then scan the QR code with your phone to get points.
    This game is in beta so keep in mind it may not work at any time.
</MudText>

<MudText Class="mt-2">
    You can only scan each duck 1 time, the app will not let you scan it more than once.
    Some caches may be worth 1 point while others may be worth more.
</MudText>

<MudText Class="mt-2">
    You must allow the website access to your location and camera to play the game.
    Please refresh your browser cache if you accidentally deny the permission.
</MudText>

<MudText Class="mt-2">
    Contact an adult staff member if you need assistance with your username or password.
    All information collected is internal and will be deleted following the completion of the event.
</MudText>

<MudText Class="mt-2">
    If you are a .NET developer and would like to contribute to projects like this please contact Xavier.
    His information can be found on the event site and on the tri folds provided during check in.
</MudText>